translate portuguese u20i_8448fa1b:

    # "For now, I should go see Kendra."
    "Por agora, devo ir ver a Kendra."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:7
translate portuguese u20i_0bb8c7de:

    # "I drive over to Kendra's house and ring the doorbell."
    "Dirijo-me até à casa da Kendra e toco à campainha."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:8
translate portuguese u20i_4fc89239:

    # "It's late and I hate to wake her, but I need to see her."
    "É tarde e detesto acordá-la, mas preciso de a ver."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:11
translate portuguese u20i_c67521f3:

    # "Kendra's Mom" "Can I help you?"
    "Kendra's Mom" "Posso ajudá-la?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:12
translate portuguese u20i_de2a91d9:

    # pc "Hi, Mrs... uh... I'm sorry I can't remember."
    pc "Olá, Sra... hum... desculpe, não me lembro."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:13
translate portuguese u20i_11072c5d:

    # pc "Can I see Kendra, please?"
    pc "Posso ver a Kendra, por favor?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:14
translate portuguese u20i_00534160:

    # "Kendra's Mom" "Oh, [pcname], is that you? I didn't recognize you. You look awful."
    "Kendra's Mom" "Oh, [pcname], és tu? Não te reconheci. Estás com péssimo aspeto."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:17
translate portuguese u20i_19dbe255:

    # "Kendra's Mom" "Come in, come in."
    "Kendra's Mom" "Entra, entra."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:18
translate portuguese u20i_44c98480:

    # "Kendra's Mom" "Kendra has barely left her room in a month, she's been so worried about you."
    "Kendra's Mom" "A Kendra mal saiu do quarto neste mês, tem estado tão preocupada contigo."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:19
translate portuguese u20i_63704f39:

    # "Kendra's Mom" "Go ahead and go up. It's the first door on the left."
    "Kendra's Mom" "Vai lá para cima. É a primeira porta à esquerda."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:20
translate portuguese u20i_008e3a26:

    # pc "Thank you."
    pc "Obrigado."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:23
translate portuguese u20i_018f49bc:

    # "I walk quietly up the stairs and into Kendra's room. She's in bed, sleeping."
    "Subo as escadas em silêncio e entro no quarto da Kendra. Ela está na cama, a dormir."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:26
translate portuguese u20i_cbba5bfa:

    # "Trying not to wake her immediately, I lie next to her and wrap my arms around her."
    "Tentando não a acordar de imediato, deito-me ao lado dela e envolvo-a nos meus braços."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:30
translate portuguese u20i_c981bd85:

    # "She jolts awake and looks at me, shocked."
    "Ela acorda de sobressalto e olha para mim, chocada."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:31
translate portuguese u20i_a0883aa3:

    # sg "[kdaddy]? Is it really you?"
    sg "[kdaddy]? És mesmo tu?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:34
translate portuguese u20i_0f0952fe:

    # "I don't answer. I just pull her close and kiss her deeply."
    "Não respondo. Apenas a puxo para perto de mim e beijo-a profundamente."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:35
translate portuguese u20i_61fcb071:

    # sg "Oh fuck, I was so worried. I thought you were gone."
    sg "Oh, foda-se, estava tão preocupada. Pensei que te tinhas ido embora."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:38
translate portuguese u20i_3005a5fb:

    # sg "So what happened? Did you see your dad?"
    sg "Então, o que aconteceu? Viste o teu pai?"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:39
translate portuguese u20i_0118c310:

    # pc "Yeah, I did. I'll tell you all about it tomorrow."
    pc "Sim, vi. Conto-te tudo amanhã."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:42
translate portuguese u20i_1cb431e1:

    # sg "I'm just glad you're back!"
    sg "Só estou feliz por estares de volta!"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:43
translate portuguese u20i_8dd76441:

    # sg "Your hair is so long! We could cut it and glue it to my bald ass!"
    sg "O teu cabelo está tão comprido! Podíamos cortá-lo e colá-lo na minha careca!"

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:46
translate portuguese u20i_ca3e5be6:

    # sg "Fuck, I've been crying a lot. I never knew what it would be like to lose somebody you loved."
    sg "Raios, tenho chorado muito. Nunca soube como seria perder alguém que amava."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:47
translate portuguese u20i_f432b969:

    # "I pull her close and kiss her again, feeling her warmth."
    "Puxo-a para perto de mim e beijo-a novamente, sentindo o seu calor."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:48
translate portuguese u20i_20c28e15:

    # sg "I missed you so much, [kdaddy]."
    sg "Tive tantas saudades tuas, [kdaddy]."

# game/Scenes/Update20/u20i.rpy:49
translate portuguese u20i_14591512:

    # pc "I missed you too, baby."
    pc "Também tive saudades tuas, querida."

